&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Learn how to use cloud computing platforms&lt;/strong&gt; : Many data engineering tasks are carried out on cloud computing platforms such as Amazon Web Services (AWS) and Google Cloud Platform (GCP). It&amp;rsquo;s a good idea to learn how to use one or both of these platforms. Here is an example of how to use the AWS SDK for Python (Boto3) to list all the instances in an AWS Elastic Compute Cloud (EC2) region:&lt;/li&gt;
